  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add halved cherry tomatoes and cook until they start to soften, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in smoked paprika, cumin, and turmeric, cooking for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Pour in dashi broth and lime juice, bring to a gentle simmer, and let reduce for 4 minutes until slightly thickened.",
    "Season the tomato mixture with sea salt and black pepper, taste and adjust if needed.",
    "Warm corn tortillas in a dry pan or microwave for 30 seconds.",
    "Divide the tomato mixture evenly among the tortillas.",
    "Top each taco with sliced red onion and chopped cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy the springy, nutty flavors."
  ],
